            <title>[LU-15030] Add /debugfs interface to monitor the sync progress between MDT and OST</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15030</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;During sync between MDT and OSTs by &quot;lctl set_param -n osc*.&lt;b&gt;MDT&lt;/b&gt;.force_sync=1&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;
